name: "A special Gift"
description: Matt was known all year as the nicest kid in Junkland. however, there was no gift left for him due to the crowds of other children at the gift event. Thinking that there will be no gift left for him this New Year's Eve, he finds a small gift package on the ground. Oddly enough, "to matt" is written on the package. He was so happy that he had found this special gift for himself that he decided to never open the gift package. He wanted to keep the gift wrapping as it was.
